    "Users describe how ChatGPT plays a pivotal role in providing answers, clarifications, and solutions.",
    "Its influence is more apparent as it actively contributes to shaping the direction of conversations and offering valuable insights, indicating trust.",
    "In February and March 2023, the portrayal of ChatGPT's influence becomes more nuanced as Twitter users emphasise its role in 'guiding' and 'assisting' users in various domains.",
